claim.claim-text:
A home appliance comprising:
an appliance body (12);
a cooktop (14) on the appliance body (12);
an oven cavity (22) within the appliance body (12);
a gas-operable heating element within the oven cavity (22) for heating the oven cavity (22) to a predetermined temperature and including a gas burner (26) and a gas mixing pipe (28) having an inlet (30) open to the oven cavity (22) for intake of gas and primary air for combustion, wherein the gas mixing pipe (28) is open for drawing primary combustion air from inside the appliance body, thereby creating a first primary airstream;
a gas supply pipe (32) for delivering gas to the gas mixing pipe (28) for mixing with the first primary airstream,;
a ventilation channel (38) extending through the home appliance body intermediate the cooktop (14) and the oven cavity (22), the ventilation channel (38) being configured to draw air for ventilation from outside the home appliance;
a ventilation fan (40) within the home appliance body, the ventilation fan (40) being in fluid communication with the ventilation channel (38) for creating a ventilation airstream within the ventilation channel (38) wherein the ventilation fan (40) is selectively operable for use during times of elevated temperature within the oven cavity (22); and
a supplemental primary air delivery apparatus or a primary air delivery system for use during ventilation fan operation to create a second primary airstream including an air conduit (52) extending between the ventilation channel (38) and the gas mixing pipe (28), the air conduit (52) having an air conduit inlet (56) in the ventilation airstream and an air conduit outlet (62) closely adjacent the gas mixing pipe (28) to direct air from the ventilation airstream to the gas mixing pipe (28) as the second primary airstream for mixing with the first primary airstream and gas to form a combustible gas-air mixture.
